# Skill: daily-task-manager

## Purpose
Maintain one canonical task list. No duplicates. No stale items.

## Rules

- One task file only: tasks/current.md
- Tasks in ## Today are the only things [USER_NAME] should focus on
- Promote from Backlog to Today during morning prep only
- When done, mark ✓ and move to a done section
- Flag any task in ## Today for 3+ days without progress

## Adding tasks

Check for duplicates first. Update existing tasks rather than create duplicates.

Format: `- [ ] [task] — [context or deadline]`
